data.description: ELIGIBLE FOR A HOMEBUYER $25O0 CHASE GRANT.  This 1908 Lavaca home is perfect for admirerers of historic architecture and anyone wishing to live in the center of the city. Vance has been lovingly maintained by the same family for over 40 years & many original features remain: chandeliers, hardwood floors, baseboards, door trimmings & more! The tall ceilings, rich wood trimmings and natural light create an elegant space. Enjoy an oversized lot with gated entries, a 2 car garage & a storage shed. Bike or walk to great food & fun in Hemisfair Park, Southtown & King William. Vance is zoned for a B&B & would be a great downtown renovation project. All blue trim on the outside has been painted grey. Be sure to heck the Features & Upgrades list for details on what has been upgraded in the home and for more details on the historic features. Valued at $555,000 on BCAD**SELLERS ARE MOTIVATED!**
